Package com.nasdaq.ncdsclient.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KafkaCluster
    This interface abstracts away knowing if the underlying 'kafka cluster' is a single server (KafkaTestServer) or a cluster of 1 or more brokers (KafkaTestCluster).
    KafkaControlMessageHandler
    Handler callback interface for control messages.
    KafkaProvider
    Provides a slimmed down view onto KafkaCluster to avoid circular references in code.
